  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="29508679">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/NeverLate/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2762173-31.jpg" alt="宋痴" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29508679/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29508679/" class="">第52页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/NeverLate/" class=" " title="宋痴">宋痴</a>
                (此事古难全。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29508679">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">费孝通和斯里瓦尼斯（Srinivas）的著作因其可读性很高而备受推崇，我认为这来自他们对自己总体趋势的把握，以及对这种把握的自信。这种把握和自信使得他们能够讲复杂的社会现象删繁就简，直中要害。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-11-25 23:03</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                费孝通和斯里瓦尼斯（Srinivas）的著作因其可读性很高而备受推崇，我认为这来自他们对自己总体趋势的把握，以及对这种把握的自信。这种把握和自信使得他们能够讲复杂的社会现象删繁就简，直中要害。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
